snippet.title: Electro Bop Boxing League Trailer
snippet.description:
A new experimental auto-battler / rhythm light boxing game scored to an Electro Swing music style! Takes place in a 1950s Atompunk Future/Retro setting. Aimed to release in Q1 of 2025. 

This project represents some of the new tech and streamlined development practices I explored over the past 10 months. As a developer I've gotten better at building modular systems with a reasonably low bug occurrence. I took on this project wanting to refine some of my skills on a blank slate and it's undoubtedly going to help with future projects such as Wastehaven.
